#

Spicy Grilled Chicken Quinoa Bowl

30 min
$15
550 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinGluten FreeDairy Free

Cuisine:

AmericanMexican

Course:

Main CourseLunch

Tags:

EasyQuickHealthy

Description

A zesty and nutritious bowl featuring tender grilled chicken and fluffy quinoa, topped with fresh veggies and a spicy kick.

Ingredients

  • chicken breast: 1 lb
  • quinoa: 1 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • cumin: 1 tsp
  • paprika: 1 tsp
  • chili powder: 1 tsp
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • lime juice: 2 tbsp
  • bell pepper: 1, diced
  • corn: 1 cup
  • avocado: 1, sliced
  • cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
